[MATLAB Installation]
1. Download the matlab installation package from
	https://www.mathworks.com/products/matlab.html?s_tid=hp_products_matlab

2. Follow these steps:
	cd ~/Downloads
	mkdir matlab
	unzip -q matlab_R20XXa_glnxa64.zip -d matlab
	sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/MATLAB/R20XXa/
	cd matlab
	sudo ./install

3. Follow the MATLAB installer instructions:
	!!! Make sure to select "Create symbolic links to MATLAB scripts" with the default repository !!!

4. To create a shortcut, follow these steps:
	sudo wget -qO /usr/share/icons/matlab.png http://bit.ly/2SUSFo3
	sudo wget -qO /usr/share/applications/matlab.desktop http://bit.ly/2vcomAf
	sudo nano /usr/share/applications/matlab.desktop

5. Remove the temporary installation files:
	cd ~
	rm ~/Downloads/matlab_R20XXa_glnxa64.zip
	rm -fr ~/Downloads/matlab